  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Roll out puff pastry and cut into 12 equal-sized rectangles.",
    "In a large skillet, heat sesame oil over medium heat and cook mushrooms and spinach until softened.",
    "In a large bowl, combine ricotta cheese, pesto, soy sauce, rice vinegar, ginger, and turmeric. Stir in cilantro.",
    "To assemble the lasagna, begin with a layer of puff pastry, followed by a layer of the cheese mixture, and then a layer of the mushroom and spinach mixture.",
    "Repeat the layers two more times, finishing with a layer of puff pastry on top.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes, or until the pastry is golden brown and the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for 10-15 minutes before slicing and serving."
  ],
